SmartBill is a web-based billing and expense management application designed for freelancers, small business owners, and independent contractors who need a simple yet intelligent way to manage their finances. The app solves the problem of disorganized billing and inconsistent tracking by automating invoice generation, payment reminders, and expense summaries.

Target Users:
Freelancers and small business owners who manage multiple clients and transactions, and need reliable expense tracking with minimal manual input.

Core Features:

AI-assisted invoice creation and expense categorization

Secure user authentication and dashboard

Payment reminder notifications

Analytics for monthly income and expenses

Technology Stack:

Frontend: React.js with TailwindCSS

Backend: Node.js + Express

Database: MongoDB Atlas

Deployment: Docker + GitHub Actions + Render (or AWS)

AI Integration: OpenAI API for categorizing expenses and summarizing financial insights

SmartBill aims to streamline financial management while giving users intelligent insights into their business health â€” all in one intuitive dashboard.
